Description: At Canton Music we don't send out an instrument that's been sitting in a warehouse for months, we send you the EXACT instrument that you see pictured. Before shipping out any instrument, we make sure it gets the approval of our in house tech, Dr. Bones. In addition to Dr. Bones' 12-Point inspection, he'll often write his own review of the instrument and we'll feature it in the description. Jackson Adrian Smith Signature SDX Dinky Electric GuitarSolidbody Electric Guitar with Basswood Body, Maple Neck, Compound-radius Maple Fingerboard, 2 Single-coil Pickups, and 1 Humbucking Pickup - Snow WhiteThe Adrian Smith SDX features a basswood body, bolt-on maple neck, compound-radius maple fingerboard, HSS configuration (high-output Jackson bridge pickup, noiseless middle and neck single-coil pickups), black pickguard (maple fingerboard model), five-way blade selector switch, Jackson tuners, Floyd Rose® Special tremolo system and black hardware. High-performance design puts you in touch with your music.For playability, you can't beat the SuperStrat recipe. Optimized electronics give you a staggering range of tone - with no noise.
